# Project Rules

- Canonical docs: `README.md`, `AGENTS.md`, `docs/explanation/scope-contract.md`, `docs/explanation/received-document-compliance.md`.
- **NeNe Vault = received-document archive only** (ADR 0009).
- Do NOT add invoice issuance, bank reconciliation, CSV presets, or expense workflows.
- Compliance changes require ADR + professional review when cited by law.
- Issue-driven; English repository docs (ADR 0008); no secrets in git.
